Class LecturerMenuController

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Menu, SceneSetter
    public class LecturerMenuController
extends AbstractController
implements Menu
    The LecturerMenuController class is a controller class for the lecturer menu GUI. It extends the AbstractController class and handles user interactions and events.
